n借左念俾王妃而王妃又真係自動可以用到<br />\n應該係同打你一拳強制開曬d精孔個效果係一樣"},{"pid":"fb0aec24d8f621bfd75793afda961d503f7df8ca","tid":373940,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T14:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又第幾私設兵 又護衛 又第幾王子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又一堆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1.人名<br />\n2.來自第x王子 <br />\n3.王子私設兵/王妃所屬兵/王子私設兵隊長/王妃所屬兵隊長/非戰鬥人員<br />\n<br />\n結論:求下你快啲殺死哂佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每次都要出返個張14個王子圖出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要有埋王妃圖先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n下次開post 果位可唔可以順便加埋條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e8bcaaf401cc58c3d3c6296c9130480445ebbe","tid":373940,"uid":11890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>櫸坂46 Silent Majority<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冨樫都係fans!? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見到都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 撚左</blockquote><br />\n我都咁諗<br />\n如果個翻譯真係用沉默的多數仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打機追星&hellip;富奸簡直係毒撚既典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/bcfcde0agy1fiv0i5qwa2j20nm0y6tms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwx4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2Fbcfcde0agy1fiv0i5qwa2j20nm0y6tms.jpg&h=453ed721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<i